    Scenario: :debug-cache-stats
        When I run :debug-cache-stats
        Then "is_valid_prefix: CacheInfo(*)" should be logged
        And "_render_stylesheet: CacheInfo(*)" should be logged

    ## :debug-console

    @no_xvfb
